edu.fresno.uniobjects.data
Class FieldSet

java.lang.Object
  edu.fresno.uniobjects.data.FieldSet

public class FieldSet
extends Object

A FieldSet is a wrapper for a List of Fields, used when returning data from UniDataConnection.getFields(FieldDefinition).

Author:
Brandon Tilley
